wardance.unyielding_spirit.desc:
You may equip {Resolution;DARK_GREEN} and 2 other colors. 
{Automatically consume 1 spirit on attack to add 6 posture damage to the attack.; YELLOW}
Every 4 spirit recovered grants 1 charge. Charges are consumed to immediately refill your evasion meter if it is not full when you are attacked.

wardance.walk_of_dionysus.desc:
You may equip up to 3 colors. 
{All stuns against you are upgraded to knockdowns.;RED} 
Fall down drunk when knocked down, creating a shockwave that deals 5 posture damage to enemies in a {5; UNDERLINE; wardance.skill.enhancement.default} block radius. 
{Automatically consume 1 might whenever possible to knock yourself down and immediately stand back up.; YELLOW}

wardance.sifu.desc:
You may equip any skill in {Dominance; BOLD, RED}, {Resolution; BOLD, DARK_GREEN}, {Subterfuge; BOLD, GRAY}, {Perception; BOLD, AQUA}, or {Fervor; BOLD, BLUE}. 
{You;RED} {take;RED,ITALIC;wardance.skill.taken_damage.desc} {5% extra physical damage for every point of negative stealth.;RED,UNDERLINE; wardance.skill.enhancement.default} 
{You follow a code of honor:; UNDERLINE, GOLD; The following apply to non-players with less than 100 max health}
{- Single combat is virtuous.;ITALIC;every 5 seconds when attacking a non-marked target, knock back and slow others nearby for 3 seconds, and mark the target for 5 seconds, causing it to become immune to knockback. While this ability cools down, you cannot sweep attack normally}.
{- The downed should be spared.;ITALIC;Cannot attack stunned, knocked down, or exposed targets. Deal 7% max health damage immediately on expose scaling with effectiveness. Health damage dealt is reduced by 15% per equipped color, with multiplicative stacking and multiplied by effectiveness}
{- You are their foe, you are their mentor.;ITALIC;All stuns are upgraded to knockdowns that knock the target back, ignoring immunity.} 
{- They will leave when they have learned.;ITALIC;On dealing fatal damage, knockdown the target for 6 seconds instead. After recovering, the target will run away, dropping experience and items once they are out of sight}
{- Teaching is its own reward.;ITALIC;You have no looting multiplier, but experience gain is tripled}.

wardance.suplex.desc:
Land two unarmed strikes on the same target within 2 seconds to grab and brutally slam the target behind you for {high posture damage; UNDERLINE; equal to 150% of your current posture}.
If the target is stunned by this attack, inflict an extra fracture. The immense force generates a shockwave that deals {posture damage; UNDERLINE; equal to half of the overflow damage} to all {enemies; ITALIC; wardance.skill.enemies} in a {7; UNDERLINE; wardance.skill.enhancement.default} block radius.
{This also consumes almost all of your own posture.; RED}

wardance.overbear.desc:
Put all your weight into the attack, {tripling posture damage; UNDERLINE; wardance.skill.enhancement.default}. 
{If this stuns the target, they are knocked down and receive 1 more fracture; DARK_GREEN}.
{If this does not stun the target, your shield hand is bound for 3 seconds.; RED}
